<br />
I don't think a 31 Ranger would survive this battle.  This guy has a ton of hit points.  With my Beastlord I eat the HT myself and that drops me to 90% (I have 4k HP with Virtue and self buffed.)  Since you don't have access to C3 I don't think you could keep yourself healed for the length of the fight.  Dual wielding Shivs from Dulak and my piercing skill at 80-90 I hit for up to 25 and I have him slowed 30%.  I have Regen3, natural HP regen of 2, and with my Spiritual Radiance spell (+5 HP per tick) I am regening at 10 HP per tick and I still have to heal myself.  With all of this the fight still lasts 3-5 minutes.<br />_________________<br />Karana Half Elf Ranger of the 48th Season
