				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Do it with a Cleric or Druid friend that is also interested in max'ing skills. 
<br />

<br />
Go to PoK, get Temperance each for 20pp, let friend take HT, he sits and meds/heals himself (and you!!)  You then finish mob.  
<br />

<br />
On respawn you take HT and let friend finish mob. 
<br />

<br />
Rinse and repeat.  
<br />

<br />
Worried about if SK can Fear?  /d each other 1st and get ready with a Root.
<br />

<br />
This kindof makes it feel like an exploit now though <img src="images/smiles/icon_sad.gif" alt="icon_sad.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="gentblsmall"></span></td>
