				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">That's not an exploit either.  SOE wants this to be a social game, two people getting together to take on a mob that neither could by themselves is what they want.  Early in the game solo'ing DB mobs is not that hard, but as you progress in levels the DB mobs become harder to take down.  I took down my first red con in NK at level 17 with a partner, but alone I would have died a quick death.<br />_________________<br />Karana Half Elf Ranger of the 48th Season
